title: Prison Break Season 5 "Not All Deaths Are The Same" Promo (HD)

json.text: Not all deaths are the same.
Some are real, some are stories.
Michael, we're gonna get you out of here.
There's a plan to make this right.

Things have changed in the four years you've
been locked up, Michael.

Seems fate has joined us 
at the hip once again.
We work together, or we die.
Prison Break premieres April 4th on FOX.
